<br>
these rules were just posted by Mythic less than 2 days ago. <br>
<br>
IMHO it's too early to tell if they will succeed or not. <br>
<br>
It's too early to tell if they actually have the balls to execute these strict laws or not. <br>
<br>
If Mythic does enforce these rules exactly to the word of the law, I would personally commend and praise them, regardless of how Draconian these measures were, or regardless of the news of hundreds of angry d00ds being expelled or disciplined from Mythic's 3 role playing servers. <br>
<br>
But if Mythic does not live up to their own ideals... then I'd have nothing but criticism for them. Because this draconian edict would amount to nothing but a lot of hot air and zero action. That builds up a HUGE expectation and a steep fall of disappointment. <br>
<br>
